Mediapipe Handlandmarks (for Static Pose):
For Static poses like alphabets and numbers we use mediapipe handlandmarks to detect a 21 hand-knuckle coordinates For each Hand
https://ai.google.dev/edge/mediapipe/solutions/vision/hand_landmarker
Mediapipe Holistic landmarks (For Sequence Poses):
For Sequence Poses like Greetings , Adjectives etc we use Mediapipe Holistic to detect total of 543 landmarks 
https://ai.google.dev/edge/mediapipe/solutions/vision/holistic_landmarker

Sci-Kit LEARN (For Static Pose):
we Use Random Forest Classifier to train a model with Numpy array 

LSTM:
we use Long Short Term Memory to Train a model for sequential signs
